  "Description": {
    "English": "A stable hydrogen isotope used heavily in both small-scale fusion reactors and neutron-scattering shield technology.<br><br>Deuterium very rarely occurs naturally. Most of the galaxy's supply comes from the processing of <span class=\"name name-technology\">Di-hydrogen</span> and <span class=\"name name-technology\">Tritium</span> in <span class=\"name name-technology\">Refiners</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种稳定的氢同位素，在小型核聚变反应堆和中子散射屏障技术中大量应用。<br><br>氘在自然条件下很少存在，因而星系内的大部分供给储备是来自于<span class=\"name name-technology\">精炼机</span>对<span class=\"name name-technology\">二氢</span>和<span class=\"name name-technology\">氚</span>的加工。",
    "TencentChinese": "一种稳定的氢同位素，在小型核聚变反应堆和中子散射屏障技术中大量的应用。<br><br>氘在自然条件下很少存在。星系内的大部分供应来自于<span class=\"name name-technology\">精炼机</span>加工<span class=\"name name-technology\">二氢</span>的过程中。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一種穩定的氫同位素，小規模的融合反應器及中子散彈防護罩科技都會大量運用到氘。<br><br>氘幾乎不會在自然界出現。銀河系中氘的來源大多都是使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">精製機</span>加工處理<span class=\"name name-technology\">二氫</span>及<span class=\"name name-technology\">氚</span>而成。"
  },
