    "SimplifiedChinese": "在<span class=\"name name-technology\">多功能精炼机</span>中将<span class=\"name name-technology\">二氢</span>与<span class=\"name name-technology\">氚</span>或<span class=\"name name-earth\">硅酸盐粉末</span>一起进行加工以创造<span class=\"name name-technology\">氘</span>。",
